### 🌌 **2️⃣ ᛃ Jera (Cycles, Harvest, Natural Time)**
- **Closest Hieroglyphic Equivalent:** 𓇶 (Star - Sothis) - Symbolizes cosmic timing, celestial cycles.  
- **Why:** Sothis (Sirius) was used by the Egyptians to mark the flooding of the Nile — a natural, cyclical event.  
- **Alternative:** 𓇯 + 𓏥 (Sun + Grain) - Sunlight and grain, representing the cyclical nature of harvest.  

